1)The nethod runs infinitely and Stack Overfow Error occurs

2)The method runs infinitely and causes a StackverflowError when the parameter is greater than 0 (positive integer)

3)public static String reverse(String str)
{
  if(str.length()==0)
  return "";
  else
  return str.charAt(str.length()-1)+reverse(str.sunstring(0,str.length()-1);
}

4)public static int count(int n)
{
  if(n==1) //Base Case
  {
    return n;
  }
  else
  {
    return n+ count(n-1);//REcursive case
  }
}

5)public static String printDigit(int n)
{
  if(n==0)
  {
    return="";
  }
  else {
    return printDigit(n/10)+((n%10)+"")+" ";
  }
}
